title: 1874 Eye by-election
text: The <a href="Eye%20%28UK%20Parliament%20constituency%29">Eye</a> by-election of 1874 was fought on 17 March 1874. The byelection was fought due to the incumbent <a href="Conservative%20Party%20%28UK%29">Conservative</a> MP, <a href="George%20Barrington%2C%207th%20Viscount%20Barrington">George Barrington</a>, becoming <a href="Vice-Chamberlain%20of%20the%20Household">Vice-Chamberlain of the Household</a>. It was retained by the incumbent.
